<br>
Oh, that reminds me... there is another minor factor that completely slipped my mind. Big nukes are inherently less efficient than smaller, faster nukes. The main reason for this is that a nuke which gains the kill will have some extra, un-needed damage attached to it (that extra above the bare minimum needed to actually kill the mob). This wasted damage (and hence mana) will not be reflected in any log. The perfect mana use would be to nuke a mob within an inch of it's life, and then have a tank poke it to finish it off.<br>
<br>
Bigger, more mana efficient nukes have a hidden cost.<br>
<br>
I'm sorry that the control numbers I used did not reflect the flat nature of the damage growth from 51-59. Unfortunately, if I'd ignored improved mana regen capabilities, then it would have been even easier to poke holes in the results, so I chose to include mana regen.  I agree that each draught should perform better than they currently do as you level from 51-59, but to keep my proposal succinct and compelling, I stuck with the strongest points and skipped over some of the valid (yet still important) issues wrt specific spells. It turns out that a blanket increase in damage has a better overall effect than tweaking specific spells. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=11279.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=11270.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=11093.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=11093.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11093.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11093.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"